org.opends.server.admin.std.server

Interface RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Configuration, QOSPolicyCfg

    public interface RequestFilteringQOSPolicyCfg
extends QOSPolicyCfg
    A server-side interface for querying Request Filtering QOS Policy settings.

    The Request Filtering QOS Policy is used to define the type of requests allowed by the server.
